  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "File Note Executive",
  "description": "<p>To provide support within the following areas:</p><ul><li>Manage File Notes including sending emails to clients and working with the Trust Relationship Managers/Trust Administrators to close the File Notes.</li><li>Liaising and coordination with Client Accounting Team and Trust Administration Team for any updates, concerns, queries or any assistance needed to/from each team, as applicable, in relation to file notes clearing.</li><li>Liaising and coordination with the respective Trust Administrator, for any updates, concerns, queries or any assistance needed on any identified reportable transactions and the completion of the required workflows.</li></ul><p>Job Scope/Responsibilities:</p><p>1. To handle the clearing of Files Notes:</p><ul><li>Generate and review weekly File Notes Report.</li><li>Work with respective Trust Relationship Manager/Trust Administrator and attend to the needful to ensure that the File Notes are cleared timely including sending of emails to the clients.</li><li>Monitor the deadline of each file note and keep track with the respective Trust Administrator and escalate to their in-charge, where applicable.</li><li>Provide update on the status to the management.</li></ul><p>2. Assist with other administrative works and ad hoc duties/projects as assigned by management/manager.</p>",
